(define/contract (special-perm nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  
  (define MOD 1000000007)
  
  (define (dp mask prev)
    (if (= mask (sub1 (expt 2 (length nums))))
        1
        (let loop ((i 0) (ans 0))
          (if (< i (length nums))
              (if (and (zero? (bitwise-and mask (expt 2 i)))
                       (or (= prev -1)
                           (zero? (modulo (list-ref nums prev) (list-ref nums i)))
                           (zero? (modulo (list-ref nums i) (list-ref nums prev)))))
                  (loop (+ i 1)
                        (modulo (+ ans (dp (bitwise-ior mask (expt 2 i)) i)) MOD))
                  (loop (+ i 1) ans))
              ans))))
  
  (dp 0 -1))
